          needs and using nutrition to maximize performance and promote
          long-term health.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm a board-certified Registered Dietitian (RDN), with a Master's in
          Sports Nutrition, and a Certified REDs Informed Provider.
        </p>
        <p>
          Ready to get started? <a href="/contact" class="simple-link"
            >Contact me!</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="links-container">
        <div>
          Jump to:
