            </p>
          </div>
          <img
            class="test-arrow2"
            src={arrow.src}
            aria-label="Click to toggle testimonial"
            title="Toggle View"
          />
          <p class="testimonial-client"><em>- {testimonial[1].client}</em></p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-unit-container">
          <p class="testimonial-clip">"{testimonial[3].clip}"</p>
          <div class="testimonial-full">
            <p>
              "Working with Amity was really helpful in planning for a big
              multi-pitch objective in RMNP last summer. She helped me come up
